text: Doreen Vennekamp (born 5 April 1995) is a German sport shooter. She participated at the 2018 ISSF World Shooting Championships, winning a medal.25 m pistol results ==References== ==External links== * Category:Living people Category:1995 births Category:German female sport shooters Category:ISSF pistol shooters Category:People from Gelnhausen Category:European Games competitors for Germany Category:Shooters at the 2019 European Games Category:European Games medalists in shooting Category:European Games gold medalists for Germany
